%% 3.2.7 View Child Bus Assignment — sequence
%% GET /api/StudentBusAssignment/GetByStudent/{studentId}?rideDate=
%% BR31: Assignments stem from PAID orders — created when admin/system configures pickup

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant SBC as StudentBusAssignmentController
    participant SBS as StudentBusAssignmentService
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Guardian->>App: Open Tracking / Trip Details tab
    App->>SBC: GET /api/StudentBusAssignment/GetByStudent/{studentId}
    SBC->>SBS: GetByStudentIdAsync
    SBS->>Repo: Query assignment + route + bus + stations
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    SBS-->>SBC: assignment DTO list
    SBC-->>App: 200 OK
    App->>Guardian: Plate, route, pickup/drop-off, time (per DTO)
